2%3Cp%3EMeitei%20civil%20society%20organisations%20have%20rejected%20resolutions%20passed%20in%20a%20meeting%20of%20ruling%20party%20MLAs%20to%20arrest%20the%20spiralling%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20and%20set%20a%2024-hour%20deadline%20to%20take%20%26quot%3Bconcrete%20steps%26quot%3B%20failing%20which%20it%20will%20take%20%26quot%3Bdecisive%20action%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20comes%20days%20after%20the%20recent%20spate%20of%20killings%20in%20the%20Northeastern%20state%2C%20which%20has%20been%20tense%20since%20ethnic%20violence%20between%20Meitei%20and%20Kuki%20communities%20erupted%20last%20year.%20In%20the%20recent%20cycle%20of%20violence%2C%20six%20people%2C%20including%20women%20and%20children%2C%20were%20killed%20in%20Jiribam.%20The%20killing%20of%20innocent%20civilians%20has%20sparked%20a%20wave%20of%20outrage%20and%20put%20the%20N%20Biren%20Singh-led%20BJP%20government%20in%20a%20spot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cornered%20Chief%20Minister%20called%20a%20meeting%20of%20NDA%20legislators%20at%20his%20residence%20yesterday%20to%20find%20a%20way%20out.%20Interestingly%2C%2027%20out%20of%2038%20MLAs%20skipped%20the%20meeting%20without%20citing%20reasons%20for%20their%20absence%2C%20according%20to%20sources%20in%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20Office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20resolution%20demands%20a%20review%20by%20the%20central%20government%20on%20the%20need%20to%20re-impose%20Armed%20Forces%20Special%20Power%20Act%20in%20Manipur%20and%20a%20mass%20operation%20against%20Kuki%20militants%20allegedly%20responsible%20for%20Jiribam%20killings%20within%20seven%20days.%20The%20legislators%20have%20also%20demanded%20that%20three%20key%20cases%20of%20killings%20be%20transferred%20to%20the%20National%20Investigation%20Agency%20(NIA).%20They%20have%20agreed%20that%20Kuki%20militants%20responsible%20for%20Jiribam%20killings%20should%20be%20declared%20members%20of%20an%20%26quot%3Bunlawful%20organisation%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20above%20resolutions%20taken%20are%20not%20implemented%20within%20the%20specified%20period%2C%20all%20the%20NDA%20Legislators%20will%20decide%20the%20future%20course%20of%20action%20in%20consultation%20with%20the%20people%20of%20the%20state%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20resolution%20released%20by%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20Secretariat%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20civil%20society%2C%20however%2C%20is%20not%20satisfied.%20Khuraijam%20Athouba%2C%20spokesperson%20for%20Coordinating%20Committee%20on%20Manipur%20Integrity%2C%20an%20umbrella%20body%20of%20Meitei%20outfits%2C%20said%20they%20had%20been%20eagerly%20waiting%20for%20the%20meeting%20of%20ruling%20party%20MLAs.%20%26quot%3BThe%20people%20of%20Manipur%20are%20not%20satisfied%20with%20the%20resolutions.%20They%20have%20resolved%20to%20start%20mass%20operations%20against%20Kuki%20militants%20responsible%20for%20the%20killing%20of%20six%20innocent%20women%20and%20children%20in%20Jiribam.%20But%20we%20have%20been%20telling%20that%20the%20crime%20has%20happened%20not%20just%20in%20Jiribam%20but%20in%20several%20other%20places%20of%20Manipur%20since%20May%202023.%20People%20of%20Manipur%20have%20demanded%20the%20state%20government%20and%20the%20legislators%20to%20fix%20responsibility%20on%20all%20SoO%20groups%20and%20carry%20out%20operations%20against%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoO%20groups%20refer%20to%20Kuki%20insurgent%20groups%20with%20which%20the%20Centre%20has%20a%20Suspension%20of%20Operation%20pact.%20Under%20SoO%20agreement%2C%20insurgents%20are%20to%20stay%20in%20designated%20camps%20and%20their%20weapons%20kept%20in%20locked%20storage%20to%20be%20jointly%20monitored%20by%20the%20forces%20and%20the%20Kuki%20militants.%20The%20SoO%20lapsed%20in%20February.%20The%20government%20hasn't%20announced%20whether%20it%20has%20been%20renewed.%20However%2C%20the%20encounter%20of%20the%2010%20suspected%20Kuki%20militants%20on%20November%2011%20indicates%20that%20the%20SoO%20agreement%20has%20not%20been%20renewed%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20civil%20society%20body%20has%20demanded%20that%20all%20SoO%20groups%20be%20declared%20unlawful%20organisations%20and%20their%20agreement%20with%20the%20Centre%20be%20junked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20government%20or%20legislators%20need%20not%20consult%20with%20the%20people%20again.%20Our%20position%20is%20very%20clear.%20Within%20the%20next%2024%20hours%2C%20we%20want%20the%20government%20to%20review%20this%20resolution%20and%20come%20back%20with%20a%20better%20resolution.%20If%20they%20don't%20do%20that%2C%20we%20will%20intensify%20our%20agitation.%20Our%20first%20move%20will%20be%20shut%20down%20the%20state%20and%20central%20government%20offices%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20COCOMI%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20in%20the%20Northeastern%20state%20has%20set%20off%20alarm%20bells%20in%20the%20Centre's%20security%20establishment.%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20has%20been%20holding%20meetings%20in%20Delhi%20and%20has%20asked%20top%20officials%20to%20take%20all%20steps%20to%20ensure%20peace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20Home%20Ministry%20has%20said%20strict%20action%20would%20be%20taken%20against%20anyone%20involved%20in%20violent%20activities.%20The%20Centre%20has%20reimposed%20the%20Armed%20Forces%20(Special%20Powers)%20Act%20in%20six%20police%20station%20areas%2C%20including%20Jiribam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20200%20people%20have%20have%20been%20killed%20and%20thousands%20displaced%20after%20ethnic%20violence%20erupted%20between%20Meiteis%20and%20Kuki-Zo%20groups%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731996300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2F4ue57gi_nda-mla-biren_625x300_19_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmanipur-on-boil-civil-society-junks-nda-resolution-set-24-hour-ultimatum-7052882%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Meitei%20civil%20society%20organisations%20have%20rejected%20resolutions%20passed%20in%20a%20meeting%20of%20ruling%20party%20MLAs%20to%20arrest%20the%20spiralling%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20and%20set%20a%2024-hour%20deadline%20to%20take%20%26quot%3Bconcrete%20steps%26quot%3B%20failing%20which%20it%20will%20take%20%26quot%3Bdecisive%20action%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmanipur-on-boil-civil-society-junks-nda-resolution-set-24-hour-ultimatum-7052882%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Scientists%20discover%20large%20underwater%20volcano%20off%20Alaska%20coast%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731996197000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-115438467%2Cimgsize-43400.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fscientists-discover-large-underwater-volcano-off-alaska-coast%2Farticleshow%2F115437906.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F115437906.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EScientists%20aboard%20the%20Coast%20Guard%20Cutter%20Healy%20have%20discovered%20a%20large%20underwater%20volcano%20approximately%201%2C600%20meters%20beneath%20the%20surface%20off%20the%20coast%20of%20Alaska.%20The%20team%2C%20including%20experts%20from%20NOAA%2C%20detected%20a%20potential%20gas%20plume%20rising%20from%20the%20volcanic%20formation.%20While%20the%20discovery%20is%20significant%2C%20experts%20believe%20the%20volcano%20poses%20no%20immediate%20threat%20to%20nearby%20ecosystems%20or%20human%20activities%20due%20to%20its%20considerable%20depth.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fscientists-discover-large-underwater-volcano-off-alaska-coast%2Farticleshow%2F115437906.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fscientists-discover-large-underwater-volcano-off-alaska-coast%2Famp_articleshow%2F115437906.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fscientists-discover-large-underwater-volcano-off-alaska-coast%2Famp_articleshow%2F115437906.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Will%20Google%20Be%20Forced%20To%20Sell%20Chrome%3F%20US%20Judge%20Amit%20Mehta%20To%20Decide%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETop%20Justice%20Department%20antitrust%20officials%20have%20decided%20to%20ask%20a%20judge%20to%20force%20Alphabet%20Inc.'s%20Google%20to%20sell%20off%20its%20Chrome%20browser%20in%20what%20would%20be%20a%20historic%20crackdown%20on%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20biggest%20tech%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20department%20will%20ask%20the%20judge%2C%20who%20ruled%20in%20August%20that%20Google%20illegally%20monopolized%20the%20search%20market%2C%20to%20require%20measures%20related%20to%20artificial%20intelligence%20and%20its%20Android%20smartphone%20operating%20system%2C%20according%20to%20people%20familiar%20with%20the%20plans.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAntitrust%20officials%2C%20along%20with%20states%20that%20have%20joined%20the%20case%2C%20also%20plan%20to%20recommend%20Wednesday%20that%20federal%20judge%20Amit%20Mehta%20impose%20data%20licensing%20requirements%2C%20said%20the%20people%2C%20who%20asked%20not%20to%20be%20named%20discussing%20a%20confidential%20matter.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20Mehta%20accepts%20the%20proposals%2C%20they%20have%20the%20potential%20to%20reshape%20the%20online%20search%20market%20and%20the%20burgeoning%20AI%20industry.%20The%20case%20was%20filed%20under%20the%20first%20Trump%20administration%20and%20continued%20under%20President%20Joe%20Biden.%20It%20marks%20the%20most%20aggressive%20effort%20to%20rein%20in%20a%20technology%20company%20since%20Washington%20unsuccessfully%20sought%20to%20break%20up%20Microsoft%20Corp.%20two%20decades%20ago.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOwning%20the%20world's%20most%20popular%20web%20browser%20is%20key%20for%20Google's%20ads%20business.%20The%20company%20is%20able%20to%20see%20activity%20from%20signed-in%20users%2C%20and%20use%20that%20data%20to%20more%20effectively%20target%20promotions%2C%20which%20generate%20the%20bulk%20of%20its%20revenue.%20Google%20has%20also%20been%20using%20Chrome%20to%20direct%20users%20to%20its%20flagship%20AI%20product%2C%20Gemini%2C%20which%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20evolve%20from%20an%20answer-bot%20to%20an%20assistant%20that%20follows%20users%20around%20the%20web.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELee-Anne%20Mulholland%2C%20Google's%20vice%20president%20of%20regulatory%20affairs%2C%20said%20the%20Justice%20Department%20%26quot%3Bcontinues%20to%20push%20a%20radical%20agenda%20that%20goes%20far%20beyond%20the%20legal%20issues%20in%20this%20case.%26quot%3B%20She%20added%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20government%20putting%20its%20thumb%20on%20the%20scale%20in%20these%20ways%20would%20harm%20consumers%2C%20developers%20and%20American%20technological%20leadership%20at%20precisely%20the%20moment%20it%20is%20most%20needed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Justice%20Department%20declined%20to%20comment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoogle%20shares%20fell%20as%20much%20as%201.8%25%20to%20%24172.16%20in%20late%20trading.%20They%20had%20been%20up%2025%25%20this%20year%20through%20the%20close.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChrome%20Access%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAntitrust%20enforcers%20want%20the%20judge%20to%20order%20Google%20to%20sell%20off%20Chrome%20-%20the%20most%20widely%20used%20browser%20worldwide%20-%20because%20it%20represents%20a%20key%20access%20point%20through%20which%20many%20people%20use%20its%20search%20engine%2C%20the%20people%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20the%20option%20to%20decide%20whether%20a%20Chrome%20sale%20is%20necessary%20at%20a%20later%20date%20if%20some%20of%20the%20other%20aspects%20of%20the%20remedy%20create%20a%20more%20competitive%20market%2C%20the%20people%20added.%20The%20Chrome%20browser%20controls%20about%2061%25%20of%20the%20market%20in%20the%20US%2C%20according%20to%20StatCounter%2C%20a%20web%20traffic%20analytics%20service.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGovernment%20attorneys%20met%20with%20dozens%20of%20companies%20over%20the%20past%20three%20months%20as%20they%20prepared%20the%20recommendation.%20States%20are%20still%20considering%20adding%20some%20proposals%20and%20some%20details%20could%20change%2C%20the%20people%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20antitrust%20officials%20pulled%20back%20from%20a%20more%20severe%20option%20that%20would%20have%20forced%20Google%20to%20sell%20off%20Android%2C%20the%20people%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlphabet's%20Google%20Bracing%20for%20Antitrust%20Rigmarole%3A%20Legal%20Outlook%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGoogle%20Appeal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMehta's%20August%20ruling%20that%20Google%20broke%20antitrust%20laws%20in%20both%20online%20search%20and%20search%20text%20ads%20markets%20followed%20a%2010-week%20trial%20last%20year.%20The%20company%20has%20said%20it%20plans%20to%20appeal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%20has%20set%20a%20two-week%20hearing%20in%20April%20on%20what%20changes%20Google%20must%20make%20to%20remedy%20the%20illegal%20behavior%20and%20plans%20to%20issue%20a%20final%20ruling%20by%20August%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%20and%20the%20states%20have%20settled%20on%20recommending%20that%20Google%20be%20required%20to%20license%20the%20results%20and%20data%20from%20its%20popular%20search%20engine%20and%20give%20websites%20more%20options%20to%20prevent%20their%20content%20from%20being%20used%20by%20Google's%20artificial%20intelligence%20products%2C%20said%20the%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20antitrust%20enforcers%20are%20set%20to%20propose%20that%20Google%20uncouple%20its%20Android%20smartphone%20operating%20system%20from%20its%20other%20products%2C%20including%20search%20and%20its%20Google%20Play%20mobile%20app%20store%2C%20which%20are%20now%20sold%20as%20a%20bundle%2C%20the%20people%20said.%20They%20are%20also%20prepared%20to%20seek%20a%20requirement%20that%20Google%20share%20more%20information%20with%20advertisers%20and%20give%20them%20more%20control%20over%20where%20their%20ads%20appear.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELawyers%20from%20the%20Justice%20Department%20and%20state%20attorneys%20general%20included%20all%20of%20those%20options%20in%20an%20initial%20filing%20in%20October%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20ban%20on%20the%20type%20of%20exclusive%20contracts%20that%20were%20at%20the%20center%20of%20the%20case%20against%20Google.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20forced%20spin-off%2C%20if%20it%20happens%2C%20would%20also%20hinge%20on%20finding%20an%20interested%20buyer.%20Those%20who%20could%20afford%20and%20might%20want%20the%20property%2C%20like%20Amazon.com%20Inc.%2C%20are%20also%20facing%20antitrust%20scrutiny%20that%20may%20prevent%20such%20a%20mega-deal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20view%20is%20this%20is%20extremely%20unlikely%2C%26quot%3B%20Mandeep%20Singh%2C%20a%20Bloomberg%20Intelligence%20analyst%2C%20said%20in%20an%20email.%20But%2C%20he%20added%2C%20he%20could%20see%20a%20buyer%20like%20OpenAI%2C%20the%20maker%20of%20artificial%20intelligence%20chatbot%20ChatGPT.%20%26quot%3BThat%20would%20give%20it%20both%20distribution%20and%20an%20ads%20business%20to%20complement%20its%20consumer%20chatbot%20subscriptions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAI%20Overviews%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoogle%20now%20displays%20artificial%20intelligence-based%20answers%20at%20the%20top%20of%20its%20search%20pages%20billed%20as%20%26quot%3BAI%20Overviews.%26quot%3B%20While%20websites%20can%20opt-out%20of%20having%20their%20information%20used%20by%20Google%20to%20create%20AI%20models%2C%20they%20can't%20afford%20to%20opt%20out%20of%20the%20overviews%20because%20that%20would%20risk%20pushing%20them%20down%20in%20search%20results%2C%20making%20it%20harder%20to%20reach%20their%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWebsite%20publishers%20have%20complained%20that%20the%20feature%20dampens%20traffic%20and%20advertising%20dollars%20since%20users%20rarely%20click%20through%20to%20see%20the%20data%20being%20used%20to%20power%20those%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegarding%20data%20licensing%2C%20the%20antitrust%20enforcers%20plan%20to%20propose%20two%20options%3A%20That%20Google%20sell%20the%20underlying%20%26quot%3Bclick%20and%20query%26quot%3B%20data%20and%20also%20separately%20syndicate%20its%20search%20results%2C%20according%20to%20the%20people.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20currently%20sells%20syndicated%20search%20results%2C%20but%20with%20restrictions%2C%20such%20as%20preventing%20their%20use%20on%20mobile.%20Forcing%20Google%20to%20syndicate%20its%20search%20results%20would%20allow%20rival%20search%20engines%20and%20AI%20startups%20to%20quickly%20improve%20their%20quality%2C%20while%20the%20data%20feed%20would%20allow%20others%20to%20build%20their%20own%20search%20index.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731996180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fi97noubo_chrome-browser-bloomberg_625x300_19_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdoj-will-push-google-to-sell-chrome-to-break-search-monopoly-7052072%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Top%20Justice%20Department%20antitrust%20officials%20have%20decided%20to%20ask%20a%20judge%20to%20force%20Alphabet%20Inc.'s%20Google%20to%20sell%20off%20its%20Chrome%20browser%20in%20what%20would%20be%20a%20historic%20crackdown%20on%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20biggest%20tech%20companies.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fwor