tform%20with%20other%20Meta%20companies%20or%20Meta%20company%20products%20for%20advertising%20purposes%20for%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20sharing%20of%20WhatsApp%20user%20data%20for%20purposes%20other%20than%20advertising%2C%20the%20regulator%20said%20WhatsApp's%20policy%20should%20include%20a%20detailed%20explanation%20of%20the%20user%20data%20shared%20with%20other%20Meta%20companies%20or%20Meta%20company%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20explanation%20should%20specify%20the%20purpose%20of%20data%20sharing%2C%20linking%20each%20type%20of%20data%20to%20its%20corresponding%20purpose%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20watchdog%20also%20said%20that%20sharing%20of%20user%20data%20collected%20on%20WhatsApp%20with%20other%20Meta%20companies%20or%20Meta%20company%20products%20for%20purposes%20other%20than%20for%20providing%20WhatsApp%20services%20shall%20not%20be%20made%20a%20condition%20for%20users%20to%20access%20WhatsApp%20Service%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20sharing%20of%20WhatsApp%20user%20data%20for%20purposes%20other%20than%20for%20providing%20WhatsApp%20services%2C%20CCI%20said%20all%20users%20in%20India%20(including%20users%20who%20have%20accepted%202021%20update)%20will%20be%20provided%20with%20the%20choice%20to%20manage%20such%20data%20sharing%20by%20way%20of%20an%20opt-out%20option%20prominently%20through%20an%20in-app%20notification.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731991320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fdlcdtomo_meta-generic_625x300_18_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmeta-plans-to-appeal-indian-regulators-rs-213-crore-penalty-decision-7052778%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20the%20Competition%20Commission%20imposed%20a%20Rs%20213-cr