ds%3F%5D%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDoglapan%26quot%3B%20is%20a%20term%20that%20became%20popular%20after%20Ashneer%20Grover%20used%20it%20on%20Shark%20Tank%20India%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20Salman%20Khan's%20remarks%2C%20Ashneer%20Grover%20shared%20a%20long%20post%20on%20LinkedIn%2C%20clarifying%20every%20comment%20and%20statement.%20He%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20hope%20you%20enjoyed%20the%20Bigg%20Boss%20weekend%20ka%20vaar!%20I%20had%20good%20fun.%20And%20I%20am%20sure%20the%20particular%20episode%20got%20great%20TRP%20%2F%20viewership.%20BTW%20all%20of%20the%20statements%20below%20are%20TRUE%3A%20Salman%20is%20a%20great%20host%20%26amp%3B%20actor.%20Salman%20knows%20what%20works%20on%20Bigg%20Boss.%20I've%20always%20praised%20Salman%20for%20his%20sense%20of%20self%20and%20business%20-%20not%20a%20single%20thing%20demeaning%20said%20for%20him%20ever.%20My%20deal%20numbers%20are%20always%20correct%20(bank%20%2F%20auditor%20verified).%20Met%20Salman%20in%20an%20exclusive%20meeting%20on%20the%20brand%20collab%20for%203%20hours%20in%20May%202019%20in%20JW%20Marriott%20Juhu%20-%20along%20with%20the%20director%20of%20ad%20(it's%20ok%20if%20he%20doesn't%20remember%20me%20-%20I%20was%20not%20a%20public%20figure%20then%20-%20he%20meets%20tons%20of%20people).%20The%20invite%20for%20coming%20as%20guest%20on%20Bigg%20Boss%20was%20not%20'unnamed'%20-%20just%20like%20the%20cheque%20for%20the%20same%20%3B)%20And%20finally%20I've%20a%20pic%20with%20him%20-%20which%20I%20didn't%20earlier%20(with%20no%20managers%20around).%20Thanks%20Salman%20Khan.%20Keep%20rocking!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fembed%2Ffeed%2Fupdate%2Furn%3Ali%3Ashare%3A7264290911088455680%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Embedded%20post%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221005%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Happened%20On%20Bigg%20Boss%2018%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20context%2C%20in%20April%202022%2C%20in%20conversation%20with%20the%20students%20of%20Lovely%20Professional%20University%2C%20Ashneer%20Grover%20recalled%20how%20he%20signed%20Salman%20Khan.%20He%20said%2C%20Mr%20Khan%20asked%20for%20Rs.%207.5%20crore.%20When%20asked%20to%20reduce%20his%20fee%2C%20Mr%20Khan's%20manager%20allegedly%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CSir%20aap%20bhindi%20khareedne%20aaye%20ho%20kya%3F%20Kitni%20maandvali%20karoge%3F%E2%80%9D%20(Sir%2C%20are%20you%20here%20to%20buy%20vegetables%3F%20How%20much%20more%20will%20you%20bargain%3F)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESalman%20Khan%20brought%20up%20this%20statement%20on%20the%20show%20and%20said%20that%20the%20figures%20quoted%20are%20incorrect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshneer%20Grover%20clarified%2C%20%E2%80%9CMaybe%20in%20the%20podcast%2C%20it%20did%20not%20come%20across%20correct.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESalman%20Khan%20fired%20back%2C%20%26quot%3BBut%20the%20way%20you%20are%20talking%20now%2C%20and%20the%20video%20I%20saw%20of%20you%2C%20this%20wasn't%20your%20attitude%20back%20then.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20shots%20were%20fired%20when%20Mr%20Khan%20revealed%20that%20he%20was%20unaware%20of%20Ashneer%20Grover's%20name%20until%20his%20name%20was%20announced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20just%20got%20to%20know%20that%20you%20are%20coming%20here.%20I%20did%20not%20know%20your%20name%20also.%20Since%20I%20had%20seen%20your%20video%2C%20I%20recognised%20your%20face.%20I%20think%20you%20should%20be%20careful%20about%20how%20you%20present%20yourself%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mr%20Khan%20added.%20Mr%20Grover%20once%20also%20called%20out%20Mr%20Khan's%20%26quot%3Bheropanti%26quot%3B%20after%20the%20actor's%20manager%20instructed%20him%20not%20to%20take%20a%20picture%20with%20Mr%20Khan%2C%20citing%20the%20actor's%20discomfort.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20time%2C%20on%20the%20show%2C%20Mr%20Grover%20%26quot%3Bfinally%26quot%3B%20got%20clicked.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A17319837000