dia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fuk-vet-kills-self-over-wealthy-clients-spending-money-on-material-things-over-saving-pets%2Famp_articleshow%2F115433100.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BGanguly%20Said%20We%20Have%20To...%26quot%3B%3A%20Kaif%20On%20What%20Led%20To%20Ponting's%20Exit%20From%20DC%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20Capitals%20look%20to%20begin%20a%20new%20era%2C%20under%20a%20new%20coaching%20staff%2C%20as%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ricky%20Ponting%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F348-ricky-ponting-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERicky%20Ponting%3C%2Fa%3E%20heads%20to%20Punjab%20Kings%20as%20the%20franchise's%20mentor%20after%20spending%207%20years%20in%20the%20capital.%20Together%20with%20Ricky%20Ponting%2C%20India%20great%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Sourav%20Ganguly%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F197-sourav-ganguly-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESourav%20Ganguly%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20tasked%20with%20the%20responsibility%20of%20helping%20DC%20to%20fetch%20that%20elusive%20IPL%20title%20that%20has%20been%20evading%20it%20since%20the%20beginning.%20However%2C%20both%20Ponting%20and%20Ganguly%20are%20off%20to%20new%20assignments%20as%20the%20Delhi%20franchise%20continues%20to%20wait%20for%20its%20maiden%20IPL%20title.%20For%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Mohammad%20Kaif%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F247-mohammad-kaif-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMohammad%20Kaif%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20also%20worked%20with%20DC%20as%20a%20member%20of%20the%20coaching%20staff%2C%20many%20mistakes%20were%20made%20by%20Ponting%20during%20his%20stint%20as%20the%20team's%20mentor%2C%20and%20hence%2C%20the%20franchise%20bosses%20decided%20to%20move%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20Ponting%20would%20himself%20admit%20he%20could%20have%20done%20better%20because%20the%20team%20we%20made%2C%20me%2C%20Ganguly...you%20won't%20believe%20there%20were%20times%20we%20could%20think%20whom%20should%20we%20drop.%20There%20was%20no%20place%20for%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ajinkya%20Rahane%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F965-ajinkya-rahane-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAjinkya%20Rahane%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Ashwin%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ishant%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F900-ishant-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3EIshant%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20even%20Hetmyer.%20Then%20when%20we%20went%20to%20the%20auction...this%20was%20Ganguly%20who%20decided%20and%20I%20must%20praise%20him%20for%20that.%20He%20said%20we%20have%20to%20back%20the%20Indian%20players.%20He%20talked%20to%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shikhar%20Dhawan%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F737-shikhar-dhawan-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShikhar%20Dhawan%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20after%20which%20that%20trade%20had%20happened%20with%20Hyderabad%2C%26quot%3B%20Kaif%20said%20in%20a%20video%20posted%20on%20his%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKaif%20cited%20the%20example%20of%20Shikhar%20Dhawan's%20trade%20from%20Sunrisers%20Hyderabad%2C%20which%20proved%20to%20be%20a%20masterstroke%20for%20the%20franchise.%20However%2C%20Kaif%20has%20claimed%20that%20Ponting%20didn't%20want%20the%20trade%20to%20take%20place%2C%20but%20was%20convinced%20by%20Ganguly%20to%20go%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20we%20were%20stuck%20still%20thinking%20if%20we%20should%20make%20the%20trade%2C%20and%20it%20was%20Ganguly%20who%20convinced%20us%20that%20we%20needed%20him.%20Ponting%20did%20not%20agree.%20He%20felt%20his%20career%20was%20over%2C%20because%20it%20was%20right%20when%20he%20was%20dropped%20from%20the%20Test%20team.%20In%20fact%2C%20this%20thing%20was%20highlighted%20in%20the%20meeting%20that%20Dhawan%20is%20a%20trusted%20player%20who%20can%20score%20500%20runs%20in%20a%20season.%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22David%20Warner%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1285-david-warner-playerprofile%5C%22%3EDavid%20Warner%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20in%20Hyderabad%2C%20and%20I%20feel%20he%20must%20have%20influenced%20Ponting%20against%20going%20with%20Dhawan.%20I%20feel%20he%20must%20have%20told%20Ponting%20that%20he%20no%20longer%20remains%20a%20great%20player.%20But%20Ganguly%20and%20Parth%20Jindal%20backed%20Dhawan%20and%20traded%20him%2C%20and%20the%20India%20batter%20proved%20us%20right%20because%20we%20had%20reached%20the%20final%20that%20season%20where%20he%20scored%20a%20lot%20of%20runs.%20So%20I%20feel%20Ponting%20might%20have%20regretted%20that%20he%20would%20have%20done%20better%20because%20they%20did%20not%20win%20a%20trophy%20in%20those%20seven%20years.%20In%20fact%2C%20Ganguly%20should%20be%20credited%20for%20bringing%20Ashwin%20to%20the%20team%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20IPL%202024%20season%2C%20Ponting%20was%20let%20by%20the%20Delhi%20franchise.%20Kaif%20feels%20DC%20must've%20felt%20that%20the%20former%20Australia%20captain%20no%20longer%20had%20game-plans%20to%20lead%20the%20troops.%20Hence%2C%20he%20had%20to%20be%20released%20from%20his%20responsibilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20franchise%20owner%20must%20have%20felt%20Ponting%20no%20longer%20had%20good%20game%20plans.%20Now%2C%20Ponting%20is%20a%20huge%20name.%20He%20is%20in%20that%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Sachin%20Tendulkar%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F14-sachin-tendulkar-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESachin%20Tendulkar%3C%2Fa%3E%20category.%20Now%2C%20if%20a%20franchise%20tells%20him%20'thank%20you%20so%20much'%20and%20parts%20ways%2C%20that%20means%20they%20feel%20that%20he%20is%20looking%20flat%20with%20his%20game%20plans.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKaif%20also%20called%20out%20a%20big%20mistake%20that%20Ponting%20made%20after%20joining%20Punjab%20Kings.%20The%20fact%20that%20the%20franchise%20decided%20to%20let%20go%20of%20top%20players%20like%20Arshdeep%20Singh%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D