se-sons-face-devil-father-in-court-as-they-speak-of-disgust-and-lost-childhood-13256272%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Fire%20In%20Team%20Hotel%2C%20PCB%20Ends%20National%20Meet%20Amid%20Champions%20Trophy%20Row%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board%20(PCB)%20had%20to%20abruptly%20end%20the%20National%20Women's%20Championship%20in%20Karachi%20on%20Monday%20after%20five%20players%20had%20a%20close%20shave%20following%20a%20fire%20incident%20in%20the%20team%20hotel.%20The%20PCB%20had%20booked%20an%20entire%20floor%20for%20the%20five%20competing%20sides%20and%20team%20officials.%20A%20source%20said%20that%20when%20the%20fire%20broke%20out%2C%20barring%20five%20players%2C%20all%20the%20other%20cricketers%20and%20officials%20were%20at%20the%20National%20Stadium%20either%20for%20matches%20or%20net%20sessions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFive%20players%20were%20in%20their%20rooms%20when%20the%20fire%20broke%20out.%20It%20has%20caused%20damage%20to%20some%20property%20of%20the%20players%20and%20officials%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPCB%20has%20decided%20to%20curtail%20the%20National%20Women's%20One-Day%20Tournament%202024-25%20in%20Karachi%20following%20a%20fire%20incident%20at%20the%20team%20hotel%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20PCB%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFortunately%2C%20no%20players%20were%20injured%2C%20as%20the%20PCB%20promptly%20evacuated%20the%20five%20players%20in%20the%20hotel%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20incident%20and%20relocated%20them%20safely%20to%20the%20Hanif%20Mohammad%20High-Performance%20Centre.%26quot%3B%20The%20PCB%20apparently%20tried%20to%20find%20an%20alternate%20accommodation%20for%20the%20teams%20but%20because%20of%20the%20Ideas%20Defence%20Exhibition%20being%20held%20in%20Karachi%2C%20they%20could%20not%20find%20a%20hotel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PCB%20said%20the%20decision%20to%20truncate%20the%20tournament%20was%20taken%20keeping%20in%20mind%20the%20health%20and%20safety%20of%20the%20players.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAdditionally%2C%20the%20unavailability%20of%20alternative%20accommodations%20to%20meet%20the%20approximately%20100%20rooms%20of%20the%20required%20standards%20contributed%20to%20this%20outcome%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20PCB%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20determine%20the%20tournament%20winner%2C%20the%20PCB%20has%20decided%20that%20the%20Invincibles%20and%20the%20Stars%20--%20the%20top%20two%20teams%20after%20four%20matches%20each%20--%20will%20face%20off%20in%20the%20final.%20The%20date%20and%20venue%20for%20the%20final%20will%20be%20announced%20in%20due%20course.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChampions%20Trophy%20Schedule%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20fewer%20than%20100%20days%20left%20until%20the%20ICC%C2%A0Champions%C2%A0Trophy%C2%A02025%2C%20scheduled%20to%20be%20hosted%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20the%20tournament's%20dates%20and%20fixtures%20remain%20unannounced%2C%20adding%20to%20the%20mounting%20uncertainty%20surrounding%20the%20event.%20However%2C%20sources%20close%20to%20the%20development%20have%20revealed%20to%20IANS%20that%20the%20ICC%20is%20likely%20to%20finalize%20and%20announce%20the%20schedule%20by%20the%20end%20of%20this%20week%2C%20following%20ongoing%20discussions%20with%20the%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board%20(PCB)%20to%20address%20India's%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%2C%20one%20of%20the%20eight%20participating%20nations%2C%20have%20refused%20to%20travel%20to%20Pakistan%20for%20the%20tournament%2C%20citing%20government%20restrictions.%20The%20Board%20of%20Control%20for%20Cricket%20in%20India%20(BCCI)%20has%20conveyed%20its%20position%20to%20the%20ICC%2C%20leaving%20the%20PCB%20seeking%20an%20explanation%20for%20India's%20stance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20the%20PCB%20is%20reportedly%20considering%20escalating%20the%20matter%20to%20the%20Court%20of%20Arbitration%20for%20Sport%20(CAS)%20if%20a%20resolution%20is%20not%20reached.%20The%20PCB%20remains%20firm%20on%20its%20position%20to%20host%20the%20event%20in%20Pakistan%20in%20its%20entirety%2C%20resisting%20any%20compromise%20formula%20similar%20to%20those%20seen%20during%20the%202023%20Asia%20Cup%20and%20ODI%20World%20Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%202023%20Asia%20Cup%2C%20the%20PCB%20reluctantly%20agreed%20to%20a%20hybrid%20model%2C%20with%20India's%20matches%20being%20held%20in%20Sri%20Lanka.%20Later%2C%20during%20the%202023%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20in%20India%2C%20Pakistan%20participated%20despite%20strong%20reservations%20from%20their%20government.%20These%20instances%20highlight%20the%20political%20and%20logistical%20complexities%20that%20could%20once%20again%20come%20into%20play.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmidst%20the%20uncertainty%2C%20the%20ICC%20has%20initiated%20the%C2%A0Trophy%C2%A0Tour%20for%C2%A0Champions%C2%A0Trophy%C2%A02025%20to%20build%20excitement%20for%20the%20tournament.%20The%20tour%20began%20on%20Saturday%20in%20Islamabad%2C%20Pakistan's%20capital%2C%20where%20the%20iconic%20silverware%20was%20displayed%20at%20several%20landmarks%2C%20including%20Daman-e-Koh%2C%20Faisal%20Mosque%2C%20and%20the%20Pakistan%20Monument.%20The%20launch%20event%20featured%20cricket%20legend%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shoaib%20Akhtar%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F381-shoaib-akhtar-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShoaib%20Akhtar%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20accompanied%20the%C2%A0trophy%C2%A0to%20its%20stops%20in%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ICC%20is%20working%20to%20resolve%20India's%20travel%20concerns%2C%20but%20a%20resolution%20remains%20uncertain.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731941460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F3o366fc8_pcb-chief_625x300_19_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Ffire-in-team-hotel-pakistan-cricket-board-ends-national-championship-amid-champions-trophy-row-7049231%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20PCB%20said%20the%20decision