nes-is-more-important-13256196%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fwestern-powers-wont-be-worried-about-kremlins-public-fury-what-happens-behind-the-scenes-is-more-important-13256196%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20Decade%20After%20Heartbreaking%20Loss%2C%20a%20Father%E2%80%99s%20Fight%20for%20Fire%20Safety%20Continues%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20evening%20of%2023%20February%2C%202010%2C%20etched%20a%20dark%20mark%20on%20Bengaluru%E2%80%99s%20history.%20A%20major%20fire%20broke%20out%20in%20Carlton%20Towers%2C%20a%20high-rise%20office%20complex%2C%20claiming%20nine%20lives%20and%20injuring%20at%20least%2070%20others.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Carton%20Towers%20tragedy%20is%20something%20that%20I%20can%20never%20forget%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Uday%20Vijayan%2C%20who%20lost%20his%20son%20in%20the%20tragic%20fire%20incident.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20parent%2C%20Uday%20found%20himself%20haunted%20by%20the%20question%3A%20%E2%80%9CWhy%20did%20this%20happen%20to%20me%3F%E2%80%9D%20To%20get%20answers%2C%20he%20and%20his%20friends%20met%20the%20fire%20department%20director%20in%20Bengaluru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20only%20call%20that%20we%20got%20that%20day%20was%20from%20your%20son%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20director%20told%20Uday.%20Akhil%20Uday%20was%20able%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F308819%2Fuphaar-cinema-fire-tragedy-hero-capt-manjinder-singh-bhinder-trial-by-fire-netflix%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esave%20many%20lives%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20the%20Carlton%20fire%20accident%2C%20but%20it%20was%20unfortunate%20that%20he%20could%20not%20save%20himself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%202636px)%20100vw%2C%202636px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FUdhay-vijayan_11zon-1731927501.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222636%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Uday%20Vijayan%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Beyond%20Carlton%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FUdhay-vijayan_11zon-1731927501.jpg%202636w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FUdhay-vijayan_11zon-1731927501-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FUdhay-vijayan_11zon-1731927501-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FUdhay-vijayan_11zon-1731927501-768x512.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FUdhay-vijayan_11zon-1731927501-1536x1024.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FUdhay-vijayan_11zon-1731927501-2048x1365.jpg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FUdhay-vijayan_11zon-1731927501-1200x800.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FUdhay-vijayan_11zon-1731927501-150x100.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-380798%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221757%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EUday%20Vijayan%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Beyond%20Carlton%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20words%2C%20etched%20in%20Uday%E2%80%99s%20memory%2C%20pushed%20him%20to%20establish%20Beyond%20Carlton%20a%20few%20months%20after%20the%20incident.%20Beyond%20Carlton%20is%20a%20citizen-led%20non-profit%20organisation%20primarily%20focusing%20on%20creating%20awareness%20regarding%20fire%20safety%20and%20ensuring%20that%20every%20building%20has%20necessary%20measures%20installed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202011%2C%20the%20group%20filed%20a%20Public%20Interest%20Litigation%20(PIL)%20in%20the%20Karnataka%20High%20Court%20%2C%20requesting%20for%20mandatory%20inspections%20of%20high%20rise%20apartments%20(15%20m%20and%20above)%20in%20the%20city.%20The%20court%20passed%20necessary%20orders%20instructing%20the%20Karnataka%20Government%20to%20implement%20the%20same.%20A%20notification%20to%20re-inspect%20the%20No%20Objection%20Certificate%20(NOC)%20every%20two%20years%20was%20also%20implemented.%20Functioning%20on%20three%20pillars%20%E2%80%94%20accountability%2C%20awareness%2C%20and%20advocacy%20%E2%80%94%20their%20efforts%20provided%20a%20different%20lens%20regarding%20fire%20safety%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUday%20and%20his%20team%E2%80%99s%20efforts%20also%20saw%20the%20sanctioning%20of%20funds%20for%20firefighters%20to%20have%20a%20separate%20fire%20inspection%20department%20to%20investigate%20when%20a%20fire%20incident%20occurs.%20This%20was%20crucial%20because%20it%20allowed%20firefighters%20to%20access%20the%20accident%20zone%20sooner%2C%20enabling%20them%20to%20investigate%20and%20determine%20the%20cause%20of%20such%20catastrophes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBuilding%20a%20fire-safe%20Bengaluru%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20the%20Karnataka%20Government%20planned%20to%20develop%20blueprints%20to%20tackle%20multiple%20issues%20in%20the%20city.%20%E2%80%9CBeyond%20Carlton%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20related%20to%20fire%20safety%20as%20nobody%20considered%20fire%20a%20crucial%20matter%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Uday.%20The%20group%2C%20along%20with%20Janaagraha%2C%20an%20NGO%2C%20and%20the%20Karnataka%20Fire%20and%20Emergency%20Services%2C%20came%20up%20with%20a%20blueprint%20focused%20on%20three%20elements%20%E2%80%94%20capacity%20building%2C%20regulation%20and%20compliance%2C%20and%20awareness%20creation%20%E2%80%94%20to%20eliminate%20fire%20accidents%20in%20the%20city%20aimed%20at%20making%20the%20city%20100%25%20fire-safe!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20blueprint%20was%20ambitious%2C%20but%20every%20plan%20had%20to%20be%20to%20achieve%20at%20least%2050%25%20of%20what%20we%20had%20envisioned%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Gopal%20Devanahalli%2C%20a%20trustee%20who%20had%20lost%20one%20of%20his%20friends%20in%20the%20Carton%20tragedy.%20Beyond%20Carlton%E2%80%99s%20fire%20safety%20blueprint%20was%20implemented.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNot%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20are%20aware%20of%20how%20to%20act%20when%20there%20is%20a%20fire.%20Through%20our%20awareness%20workshops%20in%20association%20with%20estate%20managers%20and%20the%20Bengaluru%20Apartment%20Federation%2C%20we%20can%20educate%20people%20about%20the%20necessary%20measures%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gopal%20shared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20all%20had%20previous%20corporate%20experience%2C%20which%20helped%20us%20make%20strategic%20decisions%20on%20the%20data%20collected%20by%20the%20fire%20department%2C%E2%80%9D%20Uday%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20main%20issues%20the%20team%20identified%20was%20the%20involvement%20of%20multiple%20departments%20and%20government%20authorities%20in%20a%20fire%20accident.%20%E2%80%9CMost%20of%20the%20fire%20accidents%20happen%20due%20to%20short-circuiting%2C%20which%20comes%20under%20the%20control%20of%20BESCOM%2C%E2%80%9D%20Venkitachalam%2C%20a%20trustee%2C%20elaborates.%20Building%20owners%2C%20citizens%2C%20BBMP%2C%20NDRF%2C%20police%2C%20and%20fire%20departments%20are%20others%20involved%2C%20to%20name%20a%20few.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201152px)%20100vw%2C%201152px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FFire-awareness-and-prevention-day-feb-23-Hulimavu-FS-1731926410.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221152%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20workshop%20on%20fire%20safety%20being%20held%20in%20Hulimavu%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FFire-awareness-and-prevention-day-feb-23-Hulimavu-FS-1731926410.jpg%201152w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FFire-awareness-and-prevention-day-feb-23-Hulimavu-FS-1731926410-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FFire-awareness-and-prevention-day-feb-23-Hulimavu-FS-1731926410-500x281.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FFire-awareness-and-prevention-day-feb-23-Hulimavu-FS-1731926410-768x432.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FFire-awareness-and-prevention-day-feb-23-Hulimavu-FS-1731926410-150x84.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-380769%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22648%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EA%20workshop%20on%20fire%20safety%20being%20held%20in%20Hulimavu%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%2010%20years%20following%20the%20fire%20tragedy%2C%20Beyond%20Carlton%E2%80%99s%20efforts%20have%20seen%20several%20crucial%20measures%20being%20implemented%20in%20Bengaluru.%20High-rise%20buildings%20are%20now%20equipped%20with%20better%20fire%20safety%20measures%2C%20such%20as%20appropriate%20placements%20of%20fire%20extinguishers%2C%20unobstructed%20emergency%20exits%2C%20and%20unlocked%20emergency%20staircases.%20Most%20importantly%2C%20citizens%20have%20realised%20their%20part%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F167985%2Fkolkata-metro-fire-in-train-what-to-do-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprioritising%20fire%20safety%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20are%20more%20aware.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20the%20organisation%20is%20working%20on%20Blueprint%202.0%2C%20a%20revised%20version%20of%20the%20previous%20plan%20that%20Beyond%20Carlton%20had%20curated.%20This%20blueprint%20provides%20fire%20safety%20guidelines%20for%20older%20buildings%20and%20suggests%20penalising%20measures%20like%20cutting%20electricity%20or%20water%20when%20there%20is%20a%20lack%20of%20a%20NOC%20renewal%2C%20etc.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20blueprint%20focuses%20more%20on%20the%20collaborative%20effort%20among%20departments%20and%20holding%20authorities%20accountable%20when%20there%20is%20a%20power%20mismanagement.%20With%20this%2C%20the%20organisation%20aims%20to%20balance%20policy%20regulations%20and%20citizen%20awareness%20perfectly.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20National%20Building%20Code%20(NBC)%20has%20promising%20things%20included%20as%20construction%20guidelines%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Gopal%2C%20who%20hopes%20to%20streamline%20and%20enhance%20their%20initiatives%20by%20learning%20from%20their%20past%20experiences%20and%20projects%20in%20the%20upcoming%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20Beyond%20Carlton%20was%20successful%20in%20launching%20the%20%E2%80%98B-FIRE%20SAFE%E2%80%99%20initiative%20to%20sensitise%20citizens%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20fire%20safety%20in%20residential%20areas%20in%202021.%20This%20has%20improved%20the%20community%E2%80%99s%20ability%20to%20observe%2C%20assess%2C%20and%20act%20promptly%20during%20fire%20hazards%20in%20residential%20complexes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EEstablishing%20fire%20safety%20in%20Odisha%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20Beyond%20Carlton%20signed%20an%20MoU%20with%20the%20Odisha%20State%20Disaster%20Management%20Authority%20(OSDMA)%20to%20build%20a%20fire%20safety%20framework%20for%20the%20twin%20cities%20Bhubaneswar%20and%20Cuttack.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20was%20happy%20when%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F370334%2Fsambit-kumar-das-founder-ek-asha-ngo-odisha-tribes-computers-english-maths-art-think-centers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOdisha%3C%2Fa%3E%20Government%20approached%20them%20for%20a%20blueprint.%20%E2%80%9CBeyond%20Carlton%20wants%20to%20be%20a%20force%20leading%20to%20positive%20change%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Venkitachalam%3B%20their%20credible%20work%20has%20pushed%20other%20states%20to%20adopt%20a%20similar%20model.%20Today%2C%20their%20blueprint%20facilitates%20all%20cities%20in%20Odisha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSince%20Odisha%20has%20experience%20handling%20natural%20calamities%20with%20ease%2C%20they%20were%20more%20prepared%20and%20flexible%20for%20the%20suggested%20changes%2C%E2%80%9D%20Venkitachalam%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-gallery%20wp-block-gallery-1%20wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2F279031372_5257968687558210_8385898760672421362_n_11zon-1731926307.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Workshop%20on%20comprehensive%20fire%20safety%20conducted%20in%20Bhubaneshwar%5C%22%20data-id%3D%5C%22380764%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2F279031372_5257968687558210_8385898760672421362_n_11zon-1731926307.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2F279031372_5257968687558210_8385898760672421362_n_11zon-1731926307-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2F279031372_5257968687558210_8385898760672421362_n_11zon-1731926307-500x500.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2F279031372_5257968687558210_8385898760672421362_n_11zon-1731926307-150x150.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2F279031372_5257968687558210_8385898760672421362_n_11zon-1731926307-768x768.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2F279031372_5257968687558210_8385898760672421362_n_11zon-1731926307-800x800.jpg%20800w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2F279031372_5257968687558210_8385898760672421362_n_11zon-1731926307-600x600.jpg%20600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2F279031372_5257968687558210_8385898760672421362_n_11zon-1731926307-400x400.jpg%20400w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2F279031372_5257968687558210_8385898760672421362_n_11zon-1731926307-200x200.jpg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2F279031372_5257968687558210_8385898760672421362_n_11zon-1731926307-96x96.jpg%2096w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-380764%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWorkshop%20on%20comprehensive%20fire%20safety%20conducted%20in%20Bhubaneshwar%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20advantage%20Odisha%20offered%20was%20the%20digitisation%20of%20NOCs%2C%20providing%20a%20solid%20database%20to%20identify%20violators%20regarding%20certification.%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20were%20under%20the%20assumption%20that%20a%20fire%20accident%20won%E2%80%99t%20happen%20here%2C%20which%20led%20them%20to%20be%20lethargic%20in%20applying%20for%20appropriate%20licences%2C%E2%80%9D%20Venkitachalam%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20explains%20that%20simple%20measures%20like%20planning%20the%20electrical%20load%20and%20investing%20in%20appropriate%20wiring%2C%20being%20aware%20of%20the%20switchboard%20placements%2C%20mapping%20the%20escape%20routes%2C%20placing%20a%20fire%20extinguisher%20in%20place%2C%20investing%20in%20a%20fire%20alarm%2C%20and%20most%20importantly%2C%20encouraging%20citizens%20to%20ask%20the%20right%20questions%20before%20moving%20into%20a%20building%20can%20save%20lives%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F264089%2Fdrdo-dare-to-dream-contest-winner-innovation-aircraft-accident-biodegradable%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eavoid%20such%20disasters%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20the%20basics%20of%20fire%20safety%2C%20Venkitachalam%20discusses%20two%20primary%20criteria%3A%20the%20first%20is%20guidelines%20to%20be%20implemented%20during%20the%20construction%20of%20buildings%2C%20and%20the%20second%20is%20to%20ensure%20that%20necessary%20measures%20are%20put%20in%20place%20by%20citizens%20to%20combat%20a%20fire%20accident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThrough%20our%20awareness%20programmes%20conducted%20in%20apartments%2C%20we%20try%20to%20educate%20people%20on%20their%20rights%20and%20duties%20when%20preventing%20an%20accident%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20lifeline%20for%20burn%20victims%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20COVID-19%2C%20India%20lost%20several%20lives%20to%20fires%20that%20broke%20out%20in%20hospitals%2C%20exposing%20critical%20gaps%20in%20fire%20safety%20and%20emergency%20preparedness.%20Recognising%20the%20urgency%20of%20addressing%20this%20issue%2C%20Beyond%20Carlton%20actively%20worked%20to%20improve%20care%20for%20burn%20victims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20collaboration%20with%20TD%20System%E2%80%99s%20CSR%20activity%2C%20the%20organisation%20launched%20the%20%23FireWatch101%20Project%20in%202023%2C%20focusing%20on%20equipping%20hospitals%20with%20essential%20facilities%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F266757%2Fneehaari-mandali-burn-survivor-mission-saviour-trust-kerala-ngo-inspiring%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etreat%20burn%20victims%3C%2Fa%3E%20effectively.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prognosis%20required%20for%20a%20burn%20injury%20to%20heal%20is%20time-consuming%20and%20requires%20daily%20dressing%20changes.%20This%20process%20is%20excruciating%20for%20patients%2C%20especially%20children%3B%20but%2C%20the%20number%20of%20government%20hospitals%20equipped%20with%20separate%20burn%20wards%20in%20Bengaluru%20is%20scarce.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20mission%20is%20to%20equip%20all%20government%20hospitals%20in%20Bengaluru%20with%20a%20ward%20dedicated%20to%20people%20affected%20due%20to%20a%20fire%20accident%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Gopal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20points%20out%20that%20people%20often%20visit%20hospitals%20with%20kitchen%20accidents%2C%20electric%20burns%2C%20etc.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20lack%20of%20awareness%20in%20terms%20of%20prevention%20and%20cure%20is%20high%20as%20fire%20is%20never%20taken%20seriously%20unless%20something%20massive%20happens%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20The%20Beyond%20Carlton%20team%20has%20successfully%20created%20awareness%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F262996%2Fiit-innovation-skin-spray-gun-burn-acid-attack-injury-health-tech-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprovided%20treatment%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20over%20200%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20with%20%23FireWatch%20101%2C%20Beyond%20Carlton%20aims%20to%20provide%20medical%20support%20for%20burn%20victims%20from%20below-poverty-line%20groups%2C%20create%20awareness%20of%20burn%20prevention%20through%20educational%20sessions%2C%20and%20provide%20vocational%20rehabilitation%20for%20those%20affected.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMemorial%20for%20the%20warriors%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUday%20points%20out%20the%20importance%20of%20understanding%20the%20emotional%20motive%20behind%20these%20awareness%20drives%20and%20blueprints.%20%E2%80%9COnce%20we%20lose%20the%20emotion%20of%20why%20we%20started%20this%20in%20the%20first%20place%2C%20our%20purpose%20fails%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20February%2C%20Beyond%20Carlton%20honours%20the%20nine%20lives%20lost%20in%20the%20tragedy%20by%20holding%20a%20memorial.%20The%20event%20includes%20conversations%20with%20changemakers%20and%20citizens%20working%20meticulously%20to%20prioritise%20fire%20safety%20and%20awareness.%20Musicians%20like%20Raghu%20Dixit%20also%20support%20the%20cause%20by%20showcasing%20their%20art%20form.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201024px)%20100vw%2C%201024px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FBC-memorial-2022-1731926121.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Members%20and%20citizens%20attend%20the%20Beyond%20Carlton%20Memorial%20in%202022%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FBC-memorial-2022-1731926121.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FBC-memorial-2022-1731926121-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FBC-memorial-2022-1731926121-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FBC-memorial-2022-1731926121-768x512.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FBC-memorial-2022-1731926121-150x100.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-380758%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMembers%20and%20citizens%20attend%20the%20Beyond%20Carlton%20Memorial%20in%202022%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUday%20wants%20firefighters%20to%20get%20the%20appreciation%20that%20they%20deserve%20that%20he%20feels%20is%20still%20lacking%20in%20India.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20countries%20like%20the%20United%20States%2C%20firefighters%20are%20considered%20to%20be%20heroes%3B%20however%2C%20Indian%20firefighters%20often%20fail%