-sarah-iyer-madras-animal-rescue-society%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estray%20animals%2C%20who%20often%20seek%20food%20and%20shelter%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20people%E2%80%99s%20homes.%20Chandrika%20soon%20realised%20that%20many%20of%20the%20strays%20she%20encountered%20were%20suffering%20from%20serious%20illnesses%20and%20injuries%2C%20which%20were%20often%20left%20untreated%20due%20to%20a%20lack%20of%20resources%20or%20awareness%20in%20the%20community.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20when%20she%20decided%20to%20take%20matters%20into%20her%20own%20hands%2C%20creating%20what%20would%2C%20in%20July%20this%20year%2C%20become%20her%20rescue%2C%20treatment%2C%20and%20relief%20centre%20%E2%80%94%20Indie%20RTR.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20not%20an%20NGO%20or%20a%20relief%20centre%2C%E2%80%9D%20Chandrika%20clarifies%2C%20%E2%80%9COur%20mission%20is%20to%20rescue%2C%20treat%20and%20release%20the%20stray%20animals%20we%20encounter%20back%20to%20the%20location%20we%20brought%20them%20from.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20funds%2C%20Chandrika%20relies%20on%20family%20and%20friends%20and%20avoids%20appealing%20for%20monetary%20support.%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20often%20approach%20me%2C%20wanting%20to%20donate%20food%2C%20rice%2C%20or%20other%20items%20for%20the%20dogs.%20I%20am%20happy%20to%20receive%20these%20contributions%20in%20kind%2C%20but%20I%20prefer%20not%20to%20accept%20cash%20donations.%20I%20have%20seen%20a%20lot%20of%20exploitation%20in%20fundraising%2C%20so%20I%20ensure%20that%20all%20funds%20are%20used%20directly%20for%20the%20care%20of%20the%20animals%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EKindness%20invites%20kindness%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20moving%20out%20of%20the%20NBMCH%20area%2C%20Chandrika%20initially%20rented%20a%20flat%20in%20Patharghata%2C%20another%20suburb%20of%20the%20city.%20It%20was%20in%20this%20house%20that%20she%20established%20the%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F331419%2Fgujarat-bhargsetu-sharma-started-humans-with-humanity-animal-rescue-stray-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20rescue%2C%20treatment%2C%20and%20relief%20centre%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20a%20place%20where%20sick%20and%20injured%20animals%20are%20treated%20and%20rehabilitated%20before%20being%20released%20back%20into%20their%20original%20locations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20continued%20with%20her%20morning%20walks%2C%20carrying%20bags%20of%20food%2C%20biscuits%20and%20medicines%20%E2%80%94%20feeding%20and%20treating%20every%20stray%20dog%20she%20encountered%20in%20the%20four-kilometre%20stretch%20between%20her%20residence%20and%20the%20Mayfair%20Tea%20Factory.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20I%20see%20an%20injury%20or%20a%20sickness%2C%20I%20treat%20the%20animal%20on%20the%20spot.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20quick%20way%20to%20prevent%20the%20issue%20from%20becoming%20serious%20and%20expensive%20to%20treat%20later%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20one%20of%20my%20morning%20walks%2C%20I%20was%20approached%20by%20a%20kind%20gentleman%2C%20who%2C%20on%20learning%20about%20what%20I%20do%2C%20offered%20me%20his%20space%20to%20open%20a%20relief%20centre%20free%20of%20cost%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls%20with%20a%20gratitude-filled%20smile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20first%20saw%20her%20on%20the%20street%2C%20I%20was%20out%20for%20my%20usual%20morning%20walk%20at%205%20am%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Mani%20Chhetri%2C%20the%20owner%20of%20the%20house.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20seen%20her%20many%20times%20before%2C%20helping%20every%20dog%20she%20came%20across.%20She%20would%20feed%20them%2C%20treat%20them%2C%20and%20do%20everything%20on%20her%20own.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMani%20was%20thoroughly%20impressed%20by%20the%20compassion%20one%20woman%20could%20show%20and%20the%20resolve%20with%20which%20she%20continued%20her%20mission.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20any%20dog%20was%20sick%20or%20injured%2C%20whether%20from%20an%20accident%20or%20something%20else%2C%20she%20would%20take%20care%20of%20them.%20From%20my%20heart%2C%20I%20felt%20she%20was%20doing%20something%20really%20special%20for%20these%20animals%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FtempImagenE0fBq-1731659191-500x643.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Currently%2C%20Chandrika%20and%20her%20small%20team%20caters%20to%20the%20needs%20of%20stray%20dogs%20all%20across%20the%20city%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FtempImagenE0fBq-1731659191-500x643.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FtempImagenE0fBq-1731659191-233x300.jpg%20233w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FtempImagenE0fBq-1731659191-150x193.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FtempImagenE0fBq-1731659191.jpg%20712w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-380222%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22643%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ECurrently%2C%20Chandrika%20and%20her%20small%20team%20caters%20to%20the%20needs%20of%20stray%20dogs%20all%20across%20the%20city%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20an%20interaction%20with%20Chandrika%2C%20Mani%20came%20to%20know%20that%20she%20was%20renting%20a%20place%20to%20cater%20to%20numerous%20dogs%20that%20needed%20special%20care.%20%E2%80%9CAt%20that%20moment%2C%20I%20thought%20to%20myself%2C%20%E2%80%98I%20want%20to%20h