s%20doing%20something%20extraordinary.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRight%20then%20and%20there%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20support%20her.%20Beyond%20the%20event%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20donate%20rice%20for%20the%20animals.%20The%20event%20itself%20was%20a%20success%2C%20and%20people%20also%20donated%20food%20and%20medication%20for%20the%20dogs%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlok%E2%80%99s%20gym%20in%20Siliguri%20recently%20hosted%20a%20fundraiser%20to%20support%20Chandrika%E2%80%99s%20work.%20The%20concept%20was%20simple%3A%20for%20every%20pull-up%20that%20a%20participant%20completed%20during%20the%20event%2C%20a%20small%20donation%20would%20be%20made%20towards%20Indie%20RTR.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20wanted%20to%20give%20back%20to%20the%20community%20and%20raise%20awareness%20about%20the%20strays%20in%20the%20area%2C%E2%80%9D%20Alok%20explains.%20%E2%80%9COur%20goal%20was%20modest%2C%20but%20we%20were%20pleasantly%20surprised%20with%20the%20response.%20The%20event%20was%20a%20success.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20event%20not%20only%20raised%20funds%20but%20also%20educated%20people%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20caring%20for%20street%20animals%2C%E2%80%9D%20Chandrika%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EIntroducing%20QR%20codes%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20three%20years%2C%20Chandrika%E2%80%99s%20work%20has%20become%20a%20beacon%20of%20hope%20for%20many%20street%20animals%20in%20the%20area.%20But%20even%20with%20the%20support%20of%20her%20husband%20and%20a%20handful%20of%20caregivers%2C%20the%20work%20can%20be%20overwhelming.%20To%20manage%20the%20increasing%20number%20of%20rescues%2C%20Chandrika%20introduced%20an%20innovative%20system%3A%20QR%20code%20collars.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.th