%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChandrika%20wants%20all%20animal%20lovers%20to%20continue%20creating%20awareness%20for%20a%20future%20generation%20that%20would%20be%20more%20compassionate%20towards%20animals%2C%20and%20for%20those%20who%20aren%E2%80%99t%20fond%20of%20animals%2C%20she%20has%20one%20request%3A%20%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20can%E2%80%99t%20love%20them%2C%20feed%20them%3B%20at%20least%20don%E2%80%99t%20hurt%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20Images%20courtesy%20Chandrika%20Yolmo%20Lama%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731675309000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FtempImagefPV9Zl-1731658252.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D380185%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20former%20educator%20turned%20full-time%20animal%20advocate%2C%20Chandrika%20Yolmo%20Lama%E2%80%99s%20tireless%20work%20has%20helped%20rescue%20over%20200%20stay%20dogs.%20Today%2C%20she%20walks%20eight%20kilometres%20every%20morning%20to%20cater%20to%20the%20needs%20of%20all%20stray%20dogs%20in%20her%20locality.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Arunava%20Banerjee%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A51%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F380185%2Fsaving-stray-dogs-rescue-rehabilitation-and-sharing-success-stories%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Koodugal%20Nest%20Is%20Turning%20Chennai%E2%80%99s%20Schools%20Into%20Havens%20for%20Sparrows%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNature%20is%20giving%20everything%20to%20human%20beings%2C%20but%20we%20are%20not%20giving%20much%20back%20to%20nature%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Mr%20Ganeshan%20D%2C%20founder%20of%20Koodugal%20Nest%20(Network%20for%20Environment%20Sustainability%20Trust).%20The%20Chennai-based%20NGO%20is%20playing%20a%20key%20role%20in%20boosting%20the%20sparrow%20population%20in%20the%20city%20through%20its%20unique%20efforts%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F328099%2Fpunjab-man-in-faridkot-plants-trees-and-mud-nests-for-indigenous-birds%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enest%20conservation%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20an%20agricultural%20background%20in%20a%20small%20village%20near%20Bengaluru%2C%20Ganeshan%20D%20has%20always%20held%20a%20deep%20love%20for%20nature%2C%20which%20evolved%20into%20a%20passionate%20commitment%20to%20environmental%20conservation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGaneshan%E2%80%99s%20journey%20is%20rooted%20in%20a%20solid%20foundation%20of%20education%2C%20professional%20experience%2C%20and%20a%20deep%20commitment%20to%20giving%20back%20to%20nature.%20He%20has%20carved%20out%20a%20unique%20path%2C%20dedicating%20himself%20to%20making%20a%20meaningful%20impact%20through%20conservation%20efforts%2C%20with%20a%20particular%20focus%20on%20sparrow%20preservation%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F336408%2Fchennai-floods-solution-to-groundwater-restoration-rainwater-harvesting-ancient-system-tamil-nadu%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewater%20manageme%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F336408%2Fchennai-floods-solution-to-groundwater-restoration-rainwater-harvesting-ancient-system-tamil-nadu%2F%5C%22%3Ent%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20waste%20reduction.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20interest%20in%20nature%20began%20in%20his%20early%20years.%20%E2%80%9CFrom%20childhood%2C%20I%20have%20always%20been%20fascinated%20by%20nature%20and%20deeply%20passionate%20about%20conserving%20sparrows%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ganeshan%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20As%20a%20student%2C%20his%20curiosity%20was%20nurtured%20by%20a%20supportive%20professor%20who%20recognised%20his%20zeal%20for%20the%20environment%20and%20encouraged%20him%20to%20pursue%20it%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20engineer%20to%20environment%20warrior%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGaneshan%20pursued%20mechanical%20engineering%2C%20earning%20a%20bachelor%E2%80%99s%20and%20master%E2%80%99s%20degree.%20Following%20his%20studies%2C%20he%20worked%20as%20a%20professor%20at%20SRM%20University%2C%20where%20he%20continued%20to%20foster%20his%20interests%20in%20the%20environment%20while%20also%20teaching.%20However%2C%20his%20professional%20life%20didn%E2%80%99t%20fully%20satisfy%20his%20passion.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20his%20time%20as%20a%20professor%2C%20he%20transitioned%20to%20the%20IT%20sector%2C%20currently%20working%20as%20a%20domain%20specialist%20in%20data%20technology%20at%20Coda%20Technology%20Solutions.%20Despite%20his%20technical%20career%2C%20his%20true%20calling%20lay%20in%20his%20environmental%20efforts%2C%20and%20thus%20the%20Koodugal%20Nest%20was%20born.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FIMG-20200416-WA0001-1-1731592014.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20sparrows%20enjoy%20the%20comfort%20of%20one%20of%20Koodugal%20Nest's%20boxes%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FIMG-20200416-WA0001-1-1731592014.jpg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FIMG-20200416-WA0001-1-1731592014-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FIMG-20200416-WA0001-1-1731592014-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FIMG-20200416-WA0001-1-1731592014-768x512.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FIMG-20200416-WA0001-1-1731592014-1200x800.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FIMG-20200416-WA0001-1-1731592014-150x100.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-379967%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22853%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ETwo%20sparrows%20enjoy%20the%20comfort%20of%20one%20of%20Koodugal%20Nest%E2%80%99s%20boxes%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20seeds%20for%20Koodugal%20Nest%20were%20planted%20during%20Ganeshan%E2%80%99s%20student%20years.%20He%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20began%20working%20on%20projects%20like%20sparrow%20conservation%2C%20water%20management%2C%20and%20waste%20management%20as%20early%20as%202014%2C%20during%20my%20MTech%20studies.%E2%80%9D%20He%20started%20his%20first%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F330805%2Frajasthan-bheraram-bhakhar-tree-teacher-plants-lakhs-of-native-trees-prevent-desertification%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etree-planting%20ini%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F330805%2Frajasthan-bheraram-bhakhar-tree-teacher-plants-lakhs-of-native-trees-prevent-desertification%2F%5C%22%3Etiative%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20school%20campuses%2C%20setting%20a%20personal%20goal%20to%20plant%20at%20least%20500%20trees%20every%20year.%20These%20early%20efforts%20were%20fueled%20by%20his%20belief%20that%20individuals%20should%20give%20back%20to%20nature%20in%20whatever%20way%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%2029%20July%202020%2C%20Ganeshan%20and%20his%20wife%2C%20Shanthini%2C%20a%20professor%20at%20JNN%20Institute%20of%20Engineering%20and%20a%20PhD%20candidate%20in%20mathematics%2C%20officially%20registered%20Koodugal%20Nest%2C%20marking%20the%20beginning%20of%20their%20shared%20journey%20to%20make%20a%20difference.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20marriage%2C%20my%20wife%20Shanthini%20became%20the%20backbone%20of%20Koodugal%20Nest%2C%20taking%20on%20the%20role%20of%20project%20manager%20and%20guiding%20the%20mission%20with%20unwavering%20support%2C%E2%80%9D%20admits%20Ganeshan.%20What%20began%20as%20a%20personal%20project%20had%20now%20evolved%20into%20a%20fully-fledged%20organisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Sparrow%20populations%20have%20increased%20by%2015%25%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKoodugal%20Nest%E2%80%99s%20core%20mission%20is%20to%20significantly%20increase%20the%20sparrow%20population%2C%20ensuring%20their%20presence%20thrives%20across%20communities.%20The%20organisation%20works%20by%20educating%20students%20and%20communities%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20sparrows%20and%20involving%20them%20in%20hands-on%20activities%20such%20as%20constructing%20sparrow%20nest%20boxes.%20These%20nest%20boxes%20provide%20much-needed%20shelter%20for%20sparrows%2C%20who%20face%20severe%20habitat%20loss%20due%20to%20urbanisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20insectivores%2C%20sparrows%20play%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20controlling%20pests%20like%20mosquitoes%2C%20flies%2C%20and%20crop-damaging%20insects%2C%20which%20helps%20reduce%20diseases%20such%20as%20malaria%20and%20dengue%2C%20supporting%20human%20health.%20By%20keeping%20grasshopper%20populations%20in%20check%2C%20they%20also%20protect%20crops%2C%20promoting%20agricultural%20productivity%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ganeshan%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CConserving%20sparrows%20is%20also%20essential%20for%20maintaining%20biodiversity%2C%20as%20they%20play%20a%20key%20role%20in%20seed%20dispersal.%20By%20feeding%20on%20seeds%20from%20various%20plants%2C%20sparrows%20help%20spread%20plant%20species%20across%20ecosystems%2C%20supporting%20the%20regeneration%20of%20plant%20life.%20This%20process%20not%20only%20promotes%20healthy%20and%20diverse%20habitats%20but%20also%20ensures%20the%20long-term%20stability%20of%20ecosystems%2C%20making%20sparrow%20conservation%20crucial%20for%20environmental%20balance%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NGO%E2%80%99s%20impact%20has%20been%20far-reaching.%20Over%20the%20past%20few%20years%2C%20Koodugal%20has%20distributed%20more%20than%2010%2C000%20nest%20boxes%20across%2040-45%20schools%20and%20gated%20communities%20in%20Chennai.%20According%20to%20Ganeshan%2C%20%E2%80%9CAbout%2060-70%25%20of%20the%20nest%20boxes%20are%20now%20occupied%20by%20sparrows%2C%20with%20multiple%20generations%20now%20nesting%20in%20the%20boxes.%20In%20North%20Chennai%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F251443%2Fd-ganesan-chennai-professor-koodugal-trust-sparrow-nesting-space-conservation-sanctuary-school-student-volunteer-initiative-ros174%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esparrow%20populations%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20increased%20by%2015%25%20in%20the%20last%20four%20years.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EOvercoming%20challenges%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20any%20ambitious%20venture%2C%20Koodugal%20Nest%20faced%20its%20share%20of%20challenges.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20first%20approached%20communities%20in%20North%20Chennai%2C%20people%20were%20hesitant.%20We%20were%20strangers%2C%20and%20many%20didn%E2%80%99t%20understand%20why%20sparrow%20conservation%20mattered%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ganeshan%20recalls.%20The%20team%20faced%20initial%20roadblocks%20in%20convincing%20local%20residents%2C%20schools%2C%20and%20organisations%20to%20participate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20we%20reached%20out%20to%20ten%20schools%20and%20gained%20media%20attention%2C%20schools%20began%20welcoming%20our%20projects%2C%20and%20soon%20both%2C%20educational%20institutions%20and%20local%20communities%20started%20actively%20engaging%20with%20us%20to%20promote%20sparrow%20conservation%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ganeshan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20challenge%20was%20the%20cost%20of%20constructing%20the%20nest%20boxes.%20Initially%2C%20Koodugal%20worked%20with%20a%20carpenter%20who%20charged%20around%20Rs%20200-250%20per%20nest%20box.%20But%20the%20team%20wanted%20to%20make%20the%20project%20more%20sustainable.%20To%20overcome%20this%2C%20they%20started%20producing%20their%20own%20kits.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-07-at-19.53.40-1-1731592109.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Students%20get%20training%20to%20assemble%20sparrow%20nest%20boxes%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-07-at-19.53.40-1-1731592109.jpeg%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-07-at-19.53.40-1-1731592109-300x169.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-07-at-19.53.40-1-1731592109-500x281.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-07-at-19.53.40-1-1731592109-768x432.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-07-at-19.53.40-1-1731592109-1536x864.jpeg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-07-at-19.53.40-1-1731592109-1200x675.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-07-at-19.53.40-1-1731592109-150x84.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-379970%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EStudents%20get%20training%20to%20assemble%20sparrow%20nest%20boxes%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20cut%20the%20materials%20ourselves%2C%20and%20instead%20of%20giving%20out%20finished%20products%2C%20we%20trained%20students%20to%20assemble%20their%20own%20nest%20boxes%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ganeshan%20explains.%20This%20hands-on%20approach%20helped%20lower%20the%20cost%20to%20Rs%20100-150%20per%20box%2C%20while%20also%20empowering%20students%20and%20residents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFeedback%20from%20students%20was%20crucial%20in%20improving%20the%20design%20of%20the%20nest%20boxes.%20Ganeshan%E2%80%99s%20team%20adjusted%20the%20dimensions%20and%20structure%20based%20on%20real-world%20use%2C%20gradually%20refining%20the%20design%20to%20maximise%20its%20appeal%20to%20sparrows.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CKoodugal%20Nest%20work%20would%20not%20have%20been%20possible%20without%20the%20support%20of%20its%20corporate%20partners.%20Chennai%20Willingdon%20Corporate%20Foundation%20(CWCF)%2C%20Surveysparrow%20Pvt%20Ltd%2C%20and%20Lennox%20India%20Technology%20have%20been%20instrumental%20in%20funding%20the%20distribution%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F275250%2Fdelhi-nest-man-builds-bird-bamboo-homes-trains-students%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enest%20boxes%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20ensuring%20the%20continued%20growth%20of%20the%20initiative%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ganeshan%20acknowledges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBringing%20communities%20together%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20corporate%20partnerships%20have%20been%20a%20significant%20source%20of%20funding%2C%20Ganeshan%20stresses%20that%20the%20project%E2%80%99s%20true%20success%20lies%20in%20the%20community%E2%80%99s%20involvement.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20real%20impact%20comes%20from%20students%2C%20families%2C%20and%20communities%20coming%20together%20to%20make%20this%20project%20a%20success%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPrevious%20generations%20understood%20the%20importance%20of%20sparrows%2C%20but%20today%E2%80%99s%20generation%20is%20less%20aware%20of%20how%20vital%20they%20are%20for%20human%20survival.%20Unfortunately%2C%20the%20general%20public%20often%20lacks%20the%20time%20or%20interest%20to%20learn%20about%20their%20significance.%20This%20is%20why%20we%20decided%20to%20focus%20on%20schools%2C%20to%20raise%20awareness%20and%20explain%20the%20mission%20of%20Koodugal%20Nest%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20founder%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201152px)%20100vw%2C%201152px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-05-at-22.32.15-1-1731592215.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221152%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ganeshan%20focuses%20on%20schools%20to%20raise%20awareness%20about%20sparrow%20conservation%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-05-at-22.32.15-1-1731592215.jpeg%201152w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-05-at-22.32.15-1-1731592215-300x169.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-05-at-22.32.15-1-1731592215-500x281.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-05-at-22.32.15-1-1731592215-768x432.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-05-at-22.32.15-1-1731592215-150x84.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-379974%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22648%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EGaneshan%20focuses%20on%20schools%20to%20raise%20awareness%20about%20sparrow%20conservation%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20significant%20discovery%20the%20NGO%20made%20was%20that%20the%20reduction%20in%20sand%20in%20urban%20areas%20was%20a%20major%20factor%20in%20the%20sparrow%20population%20decline.%20In%202020%2C%20at%20Revoor%20Padmanabha%20Chetty%20Matriculation%20Higher%20Secondary%20School%20in%20Tiruvottiyur%2C%20the%20abundance%20of%20sand%20made%20it%20the%20perfect%20environment%20for%20sparrows.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20installing%20100%20nest%20boxes%20on%20the%20school%20campus%2C%20the%20results%20were%20immediate.%20%E2%80%9CWithin%20six%20months%2C%20most%20of%20the%20boxes%20were%20occupied%2C%20and%20today%2C%20100%25%20of%20the%20nest%20boxes%20are%20in%20use%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ganeshan%20proudly%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20dedicate%20our%20time%20to%20conserving%20sparrows%20because%20as%20their%20population%20grows%2C%20they%20will%20help%20control%20mosquitoes%2C%20cockroaches%2C%20and%20other%20small%20insects%20that%20often%20go%20unnoticed.%20Sparrows%20thrive%20close%20to%20human%20settlements%2C%20as%20they%20can%20only%20survive%20in%20temperatures%20that%20are%20ideal%20for%20us%2C%20not%20in%20extremes%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EEmpowering%20the%20next%20generation%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKoodugal%20Trust%20has%20made%20a%20significant%20impact%20on%20students.%20Sharing%20her%20experience%2C%20Prayukta%2C%20a%2014-year-old%20student%20from%20RPC%20Matriculation%20School%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20father%20was%20a%20part%20of%20the%20Koodugal%20Nest%20project%2C%20and%20he%20brought%20home%20a%20nest%20in%202022.%20We%20all%20helped%20in%20installing%20it%2C%20and%20it%20was%20amazing%20to%20watch%20sparrows%20take%20care%20of%20their%20young%20ones.%20I%20have%20developed%20a%20habit%20of