year-old%20Aryan%20took%20the%20leap%20and%20started%20LaunchPad%20as%20a%20club%20at%20his%20school.%20What%20began%20as%20a%20small%20group%20of%20students%20learning%20how%20to%20build%20real-world%20projects%20soon%20expanded%20into%20a%20global%20initiative.%20Now%2C%20less%20than%20two%20years%20later%2C%20LaunchPad%20has%20scaled%20beyond%20a%20school%20club%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F295026%2Fhealthcare-startup-to-manage-pcos-for-indian-women-by-sisters-raises-funding%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edigital%20platform%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20serves%20students%20across%2015%20schools%20in%20five%20countries.%20Today%2C%20the%20team%20has%20expanded%20to%20a%20dynamic%20group%20of%2015%20to%2020%20young%20individuals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELaunchPad%E2%80%99s%20mission%20is%20simple%3A%20to%20help%20students%20between%20the%20ages%20of%2012%20and%2017%20learn%20essential%20skills%20and%20gain%20hands-on%20experience%20in%20project%20development.%20But%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20just%20about%20learning%20how%20to%20code%20or%20design.%20LaunchPad%20focuses%20on%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20future-proof%20skills%20that%20are%20vital%20in%20today%E2%80%99s%20fast-changing%20world.%20These%20include%20design%20thinking%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F337031%2Fbest-ai-innovations-by-indians-artificial-intelligence-startup%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eartificial%20intelligence%20foundations%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20business%20fundamentals%2C%20storytelling%20and%20communication%2C%20and%20financial%20literacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20are%20the%20skills%20that%20will%20be%20relevant%20no%20matter%20what%20career%20path%20students%20choose%2C%E2%80%9D%20Aryan%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CThey%E2%80%99re%20the%20building%20blocks%20for%20anything%20they%20want%20to%20create%20in%20the%20future.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn