20are%20some%20of%20the%20problem%20statements%20startups%20incubated%20at%20thingQbator%2C%20have%20solved%20using%20technology.%20This%20programme%20has%20enabled%20students%20to%20transform%20their%20ideas%20into%20thriving%20ventures%20through%20guidance%2C%20mentorship%2C%20and%20funding%20%E2%80%94%20encouraging%20them%20to%20become%20job%20creators%20rather%20than%20job%20seekers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20CSR%20initiative%20by%20Cisco%2C%20in%20partnership%20with%20nasscom%20foundation%20under%20the%20Social%20Innovation%20For%20Youth%20(SIFY)%20initiative%2C%20thingQbator%20provides%20a%20platform%20for%20young%20minds%20to%20be%20nurtured%20and%20transformed%20into%20future-ready%20creators.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20platform%20serves%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98mind%20gym%E2%80%99%2C%20where%20students%20can%20engage%20in%20a%20dynamic%20learning%20cycle%20enriched%20with%20mentorship%20programmes%20and%20workshops.%20These%20programmes%20cover%20a%20range%20of%20topics%20%E2%80%94%20from%20current%20to%20emerging%20technologies%20and%20entrepreneurial%20skills%20%E2%80%94%20ensuring%20participants%20are%20well-prepared%20for%20the%20complexities%20of%20modern%20business%20and%20technological%20landscapes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERostow%20Ravanan%2C%20chairperson%20of%20nasscom%20foundation%2C%20highlights%2C%20%E2%80%9CAt%20nasscom%20foundation%2C%20we%20believe%20in%20the%20transformative%20power%20of%20technology%20and%20innovation%20to%20address%20pressing%20societal%20challenges.%20thingQbator%20is%20a%20testament%20to%20this%20belief%2C%20providing%20young%20innovators%20with%20the%20tools%2C%20mentorship%2C%20and%20resources%20they%20need%20to%20turn%20their%20ideas%20into%20impactful%20solutions.%20From%20enhancing%20agricultural%20practices%20to%20empowering%20the%20visually%20impaired%2C%20some%20of%20the%20innovations%20are%20inspiring%20and%20underscore%20the%20importance%20of%20nurturing%20the%20next%20generation%20of%20problem-solvers.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E